data.description: Experience the epitome of loft living in Boston's prestigious Seaport neighborhood, complete with two deeded garage parking spaces. Revel in the expansive 11+ ceilings, pristine concrete finishes on floors & walls, complemented by the timeless charm of industrial mushroom columns. The kitchen, crafted by the acclaimed Downsview Kitchens, boasts premium Miele & Subzero appliances, a commercial-grade wine fridge, and elegant marble countertops. Luxuriate in bathroom adorned with top-tier fixtures by Duravit and Grohe, and enjoy the bespoke touch of custom barn doors throughout the space. If desired, there's potential to add a second bedroom. Common roof deck offers a perfect spot for relaxation and entertainment. Ideally located to all the Seaport has to offer including the Lawn on D, Seaport Waterfront, restaurants, shops & public transit. Easy access to the Financial District, highways & airport. this residence truly feels like coming home. Welcome to sophisticated urban living!
